Package timelineManager.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractController
    This class is an abstract controller which is a parent to all controllers in the timeline manager application.
    AddTaskController
    This is a controller class for the AddTimelineView.
    AddTimelineController
    This is a controller class for the AddTimelineView.
    EditTaskController
    This is a controller class for an FXML window which is used to edit Tasks
    EditTimelineController
    A controller class for editing the timeline.
    HelpManualController
    This class is used to show the Manual/Help in a window to the user.
    LoginController
    This is a login controller for the login .fxml this class are to be implemented later.
    MainWindowController
    This class is the controller class for MainView.fxml It holds all logics for user interface such as on screen buttons.
    ModelAccess  
    MoveTimelineController
    This class moves the timeline and all tasks in the timeline x many days forward or backward.
